{"tid":2348900,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"各位家長請注意 而家唔撚識教仔都自動被歸類做藍絲支那蝗 請注意管教貴子弟 免得被視作賤民看待","createTime":"2021-01-01T06:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T14:00:45.000Z","uid":388757,"like":51,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"718445fbefabd1a0424cfd3d2d1324e2c9797b07","tid":2348900,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:23:30.000Z","msg":"屯門華都商場一黃店遭兩名小朋友偷竊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2348736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2348736</a><br />\n<br />\n頭幾個留言已經同個細路斷哂六親 藍絲孽種 新移民蝗蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD細路一定係藍絲上左黃藍地圖查完知果間係黃店先黎偷野 而唔係老豆老母唔識教啦<br />\n<br />\n原來唔識教仔=藍絲=蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地黃絲老豆老母個個都勁撚識教仔 不過唔知點解連登隔幾日就一堆呻老豆老母既垃圾post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時就假惺惺 咩我們沒有分化的本錢 咩梁天琦語錄 要團結唔同光譜諸如此類<br />\n<br />\n實際就搞埋d黃衛兵沙文主義 我地香港人個個都道德滿分 唔會做呢d野 <br />\n<br />\n所有做壞事既 道德感唔夠正義既一律係藍絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解唔信木耳係一條仆街？ 因為佢著港獨tee周街行 手足黎架 有咩可能係仆街<br />\n<br />\n點解踢爆流亡班人呃課金 拎家長錢係英國租大屋吸毒會比人話分化 話熱狗？ 因為佢地係黃絲 有咩可能係仆街？<br />\n<br />\n點解基爾明明話兩個人抵死 有d傻閪係都要衝出黎幫佢兜 藍色窗簾mode咁話基爾原意係講緊乜柒野波台狗拿卡係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n因為每當佢地一路見到一個人高調地黃 有一日忽然發覺原來對方私底下係仆街 佢地既心理不平衡同埋對世界天真爛漫既認知就會被打破 <br />\n<br />\n佢地既世界一次又一次崩潰 唔好彩的話會令你落得同渣哥 Rose Ma 達哥 一樣下場 藍店熱狗人渣偽黃 所有人格謀殺形容詞都可以冠係你頭上<br />\n<br />\n美心伍淑清話放棄香港年輕人就罪大惡極<br />\n<br />\n連登一句藍絲蝗就放棄兩個香港年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地黃衛兵偉大光明正確 民主與自由萬世都不朽喎 你係咪敢話唔支持我地既偉大理想？"},{"pid":"f701d144e1915cf391afd5d9b5f490701a5e4131","tid":2348900,"uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"樓主用哂出po quota<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ed75aa3f8bbcdfca6e892684b88bd9d746e6ea","tid":2348900,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"我岩岩都想開po講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2d8e8bf8d19aa3edd1cc812cacc31d171ae1f9","tid":2348900,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"bca8dcf5dc36fb6d1c05915c8017dc38b1595034","tid":2348900,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56e2148ee8c0c397ef5736f5f0406ca3a098c4db","tid":2348900,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f701d144e1915cf391afd5d9b5f490701a5e4131","tid":2348900,"uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"樓主用哂出po quota<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"唔好笑 我地p牌仔已經好慘"},{"pid":"d4e305a393a4566950ef0725d0948140f449833a","tid":2348900,"uid":51469,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"陳彥霖阿媽都唔識教女<br />\n咁彥霖係黃定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4295abeca27994cc9e5124ef668dd90a234ae428","tid":2348900,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:40:59.000Z","msg":"Cctoy大軍入侵前留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fa226de795ba5a12ebffa5f47ce419662ee326",